{"type": "article", "id": 18995, "title": "橄榄油包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-14T07:40:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071042142La14qzBJXH70vEg.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这瓶橄榄油包装上的叶子图案是可以立起来的，立刻让这瓶橄榄油有了生机。浅棕色的牛皮纸上只有白色和绿色两种颜色，叶子就是用白色的线条勾出纹路来，清新而简单。放在货架上不仅非常特别，还能吸引人们与之互动，顺便带走一瓶。设计来自克罗地亚的 Izvorka Jurić，她想以此表达源于自然的想法。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145718JACgVWfk6EzmLDP7.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145719yWgbHoB35IeLSQMF.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"793\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145720ND7ynIdkxOo3YcUQ.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"488\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.45185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}